- Core orchestrator located in `core/orchestrator/`
- FastAPI API with agents and MCP servers
- Database layers: PostgreSQL (relational), Weaviate (vector/semantic)
- All database access through shared.database.UnifiedDatabase
- Deployment managed with Pulumi on Vultr
- NO MongoDB, Redis, or DragonflyDB (legacy references should be ignored)
